HEADWORD: Adipic
<hw>A*dip"ic</hw> <pr>(⟦adot⟧*d⟦icr⟧p"⟦icr⟧k)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>adeps</ets>, <ets>adipis</ets>, fat.]</ety>
<fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to, or derived from, fatty or oily
substances; -- applied to certain acids obtained from fats by the action
of nitric acid.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>adipic acid</ent>⟦br⟧
